lead_paragraph: Jamie Patrick scored 21 points and No. 22 Colorado State routed Air Force 81-48 Friday night to clinch the Mountain West Conference title and its 25th straight victory.

headline.print_headline: No. 22 Colorado State Women Rout Air Force 81-48
